CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 31, 1959, page 5, reads: "Judge Receives Pin - On behalf of the staff of Juvenile Court, Judge Gustav L. Schramm center, is presented a 25-year service pin by Gaddiel Goode, chairman of the Juvenile Court staff, while Col. Ralph T. Miller, toastmaster for testimonial banquet, looks on. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Col. Ralph T. Miller watches as Judge Gustav L. Schramm presents a 25 year service pin to Gaddiel Goode, on behalf of the Juvenile Court staff during testimonial banquet, Webster Hall
